"TC-CSR-233-POS-001","TS-CSR-233-001","CSR-233","POS","High","Staging environment with pre-change dataset snapshot available; access to ETL SQL/views and sample data containing IRCA, driver, and premium records.","1. Retrieve sample datasets used by the current ETL (drivers, premium, pc_policylocation).
2. Run pre-change query (LEFT JOIN between driver and premium) and save results.
3. Modify query to use INNER JOIN and run it against the same sample dataset.
4. Filter result set to IRCA records where policy/business addr previously caused exclusion (QC/BC cases).
5. Compare counts and sample rows between LEFT JOIN and INNER JOIN outputs.","INNER JOIN output includes IRCA records that were previously missing under LEFT JOIN for matching driver+premium cases. For sample QC/BC vehicle locations, IRCA records are present and fields (policy id, vehicle id, risk_province) are populated. No unexpected additional exclusions are observed.","temp_word_images/image1.png; temp_word_images/image2.png","Verifies AC-001.1 and AC-001.3"

