"TC-CSR-233-REG-001","TS-CSR-233-001","CSR-233","REGRESSION","High","Baseline dataset snapshot (pre-change) and post-change outputs accessible for reconciliation.","1. Run the full ETL process pre-change (baseline) and capture counts for affected tables (IRCA, Drivers SDM).
