"TC-CSR-233-BACKFILL-001","TS-CSR-233-004","CSR-233","BACKFILL","High","Backfill script available; staging area for updates; baseline snapshot for reconciliation.","1. Run backfill in dry-run mode against historical data; do not commit changes.
