3. Review report with stakeholders; if accepted, run backfill in commit mode.
4. Re-run reconciliation and verify idempotence by running commit mode a second time (no additional changes should occur).","Dry-run report demonstrates expected changes without committing. Commit run updates historical records with recalculated `risk_province`. Re-running commit mode produces no further changes (idempotent). Reconciliation report attached to PR.","temp_word_images/image5.png","Covers AC-004.1 to AC-004.3; includes AC-004.4 rollout verification"

